<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to ARP Networks</title>
    <style>
        /* Modern, clean email styles */
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Inter', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 24px 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 32px;
        }

        .credentials-box {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .credentials-box h4 {
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
            color: #0f172a;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .credential-row {
            display: block;
        }

        .label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #64748b;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 160px;
        }

        .value {
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Consolas', monospace;
            color: #0f172a;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .important-notice {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            color: #dc2626;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 16px 0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        p {
            margin: 12px 0;
            color: #334155;
        }

        a {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .order-info {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to ARP Networks!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <%= @account.display_name %>,</p>

            <div class="order-info">
                <p>Your order has been placed successfully and we are working on provisioning your services.</p>

                <p>If you ordered a VPS, expect to receive your VPS welcome packet within 24 hours or less.</p>

                <p>If you ordered an ARP Thunderâ„¢ Cloud Dedicated Server, expect to receive an email from us with an ETA on your server setup within 8 hours.</p>

                <p>Please note your credit card has not been charged and we will only do so immediately prior to setting up your services. You will receive an email receipt when this happens.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="credentials-box">
                <h4>Your Portal Login Credentials</h4>
                <div class="credential-row">
                    <span class="label">Username:</span>
                    <span class="value"><%= @login %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-row">
                    <span class="label">Temporary Password:</span>
                    <span class="value"><%= @password %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-row">
                    <span class="label">Portal URL:</span>
                    <span class="value"><%= link_to root_url, root_url %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="important-notice">
                Important: For security reasons, please change your password immediately after logging in.
            </div>

            <p>Should you have any questions or want to make any changes to your order, simply reply to this email.</p>

            <p>Thank you for choosing ARP Networks!</p>

            <%= render partial: 'mailer/signatures/support' %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 